Taken from Example and Test Vector for the ChaCha20 Cipher of https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc8439#section-2.4.2

To test yourself here is the key, nonce, and counter below.

Hex key: 000102030405060708090A0B0C0D0E0F101112131415161718191A1B1C1D1E1F

Hex nonce: 000000000000004A00000000

Linux command: chacha -e plain1.txt -k 000102030405060708090A0B0C0D0E0F101112131415161718191A1B1C1D1E1F -n 000000000000004A00000000

The md5sum of the encrypted output file should be c7a1a3b904d5ff5e08cd0106b850b00e
